text: Gustaf Armgarth (1 February 1879 - 3 March 1930) was a Swedish fencer. He competed in the individual foil and sabre events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1879 births Category:1930 deaths Category:Swedish male fencers Category:Swedish foil fencers Category:Swedish sabre fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Sweden Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:People from Tomelilla Municipality
